      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems from ASME V&V 10 suite were used to verify the linear-elastic FEA solver implementation. Patch tests and manufactured-solution checks confirm correct code behavior."
    },
    {
