      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear-elastic continuum mechanics with frictional contact is the accepted model form for ASTM F1717 quasi-static loading. Model form assumptions documented and justified relative to the physical phenomena of interest."
    },
