      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Material properties derived from coupon testing of the same Ti-6Al-4V lot used in the physical constructs. UHMWPE block properties taken from supplier datasheet with uncertainty bounds propagated through sensitivity analysis."
