      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "N=11 physical constructs assembled from production-representative hardware. Sample dimensions measured by CMM and confirmed within drawing tolerances; dimensional inputs fed directly into specimen-specific FEA models."
    },
    {
