      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Only a single compressive load level was applied per ASTM F1717 protocol; multi-level or fatigue loading was not evaluated. This limits the achieved level to 2, one below the required level of 3. Risk accepted by the assessment team given the regulatory submission scope."
    },
