      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Traceability matrix maps each simulation input parameter to its experimental counterpart. Friction coefficients calibrated from independent tribology measurements; torque preload converted to equivalent bolt tension analytically."
