      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities replicate the geometry, materials, loading mode, and boundary conditions of the intended computational use. Ensemble approach across three independent modeling teams increases confidence in result generalizability."
