    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) was reviewed and accepted by the assessment team given that the ASTM F1717 protocol prescribes a single load condition and the regulatory submission does not require fatigue characterization at this stage. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for the intended submission.",
